ast.name: RPN Calculator
ast.comment: A HP-like pocket calculator with a four-level stack and reverse polish notation (see http://www.hpmuseum.org/rpn.htm). REG toggles between one and ten addressable storage registers. "FIX . number" toggles between "," and "." as the decimal symbol. 2012-09-25: 8 correlation functions to choose from instead of 4. New FIT function finds best fitting correlation function. Plus some minor refinements.

body.text: Visual feedback for the pressed key:
1: transform (x,y) to (x',y') after entering a point
2: transform (a',b') to (a,b) after calculating the linear regression

thenBody.text: linear form is: ln y = ln a + bx
linear form is: ln y = ln a + b ln x
plot spikes to the original data points
